Package qupath.ext.braian

Record Class PartialClassifier<T>

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
qupath.ext.braian.PartialClassifier<T>
Record Components:
classifier - an object classifier
annotations - the annotations to which contained detection solely apply the classifier. If null, it applies it to the whole image.
public record PartialClassifier<T>(qupath.lib.classifiers.object.ObjectClassifier<T> classifier, Collection<qupath.lib.objects.PathAnnotationObject> annotations) extends Record
Creates a classifier to apply to an instance of AbstractDetections
